title: Black XP 6.2 Gold Final
description:
I noticed my fav version of Black XP was not available.  Big ups to Waredeamon for 
creating this release, not sure why you are gone.

This release has been flamed for viruses, worms, etc, but they are considered by most to be false positives.  That being said, I suggest you uninstall the Toolbar as that thing is suspicious.

I have always burned this with UltraIso without any problems.

See the nfo for release notes from the creator.
